Key design decisions:

Spotlight uses only SplitLeftTemplate — no other templates
No clusters, no must-read, no carousels — just hero + grid
All spotlight components are in src/components/Spotlight/ — fully independent from blog
Types reused from @/types/blog — no duplication needed
spotlight.ts has its own cache, own directory constant, own function names
